parameters:
Oh, welcome! Are you staying again!? It's 10G per night, you
know!
I will stay for one night!

Are you saying you don't have money...!? Even though you're
young, you're struggling...!! I have no choice...!! Stay the
night!!!
Oh, I see!! Please come again!!!

\SE\SE[0] Um... Two females. \!\SE[0] Please stay for one
night.

Oh, staying here for one night, huh? Are you ladies on your
way to That Place? Are you heading to Yurisene?

Well, there are a lot of female couples around here! This
area has many customers like that!

That's right! Our specialty is providing services that are
popular among women! I'm confident about it! Tell me
anything you want!

I'll prepare a room with a beautiful view! This is the most
highly recommended room here! I'm sure you ladies will love
it!

\SE\SM[nod]\SE[15]Thank you very much. \SM[nod]\SE[15]I'm
sure she will be happy too.

\SE[0]... Um, Laura? Shall we go? \SM[nod]\SE[16] Come this
way?

Oh, I forgot to mention something important...!! Have you
ever thought that this window that appears when you talk is
too obstructive!?

\SE[99]Um...? \SE[0]There's nothing in particular at the
moment...

I see!! But, there might come a time when it will be useful,
so let's practice a little right here!

First, when you want to erase it, use the right-click of the
mouse!! \. When you want to bring it back, try pressing it
one more time!! \! I don't know if you mess around with that
area! \. I'm sorry!! \! ...How is it! Did it disappear!?

\SE[1]Oh...! \. It feels like the visible area has become
wider...!

By the way, let me teach you one more thing!! \! I asked an
important question, but I forgot what it was. What do you do
in a situation like that, miss!?

That's right! But don't blame yourself!! When that happens,
try pressing the W button! It will display the previous log!
If you mess with the settings... as usual!!

\SE[17]This is convenient, isn't it? \!\SE[22]Thank you very
much for your kindness!

Alright...!! \! I'm sorry for keeping you! Take your time
and relax...!!!
Hehe... You're really kind, aren't you?
\SE[29]Ahaha... I'm not sure what I would use it for though.

\SE\SE[10]I hope it will be useful. \.\SE[10]I also plan to
use it right after this.

\SE\SE[51]It's almost time for Yuriseen.... It's way more
urban than the village, so \SE[15]I'm really looking forward
to it. \SE[2]............\SE[51].......
